### **🖥 Key Embedded AI Hardware**

✅ **Qualcomm RB3 Gen 2** – AI inference for **smartphones, IoT, and robotics**.  
✅ **Google Coral Edge TPU** – **Machine learning acceleration** for IoT devices.  
✅ **NVIDIA Jetson** – **Embedded GPU computing** for robotics & industrial AI.  
✅ **Apple Neural Engine (ANE)** – AI computations **inside iPhones & iPads**.  
✅ **Raspberry Pi + AI accelerators** – Low-cost AI inference at the edge.

⚠️ **Ethical Risk:** Proprietary AI hardware **locks developers into Big Tech ecosystems**, limiting open-source alternatives.

**Related Notes:** [[ai-ml-hardware-ai-integration]] | [[ai-infrastructure-equity]]

---

### **🔬 The Future of Embedded AI**

✅ **TinyML** – AI models optimized for **low-power microcontrollers**.  
✅ **Neuromorphic Computing** – AI hardware inspired by **biological neural networks**.  
✅ **Federated Learning** – AI training **directly on devices** without sending data to the cloud.  
✅ **Secure AI Processors** – Specialized chips for **privacy-first AI applications**.

⚠️ **Ethical Risk:** AI models trained **on-device** may still **inherit biases from flawed datasets**.

